name: ar-house-of-representatives-viewer
notes: The Arkansas House of Representatives has 100 Members, representing 100 separate districts statewide. We are pleased to provide you a quick and easy way to locate the representative from your district. Click on the map or enter your address to find who represents you. You must enter your street address, city, state, and zip code, ALL separated by commas. (Example: 000 South Main Street, Little Rock, Arkansas, 72201). House districts appear outlined in red. You can also view statewide Senate, congressional, fire and school districts by clicking on the "District" tab and selecting a category. To view maps showing topographical, image, or street-level information, select from the "Map Types" tab.
